(12, 'specialitati', 'Specialties', '<h1>Specialităţi</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Elevii &icirc;şi fac studiile la următoarele specialităţi:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<center><table class="speci">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th rowspan="2" scope="row">Nr. d/o</th>\r\n			<td rowspan="2">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;"><strong>Denumirea specialităţii </strong></div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<th colspan="4">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">Anii de studii</div>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th rowspan="2">\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">Profilul studiilor liceale</div>\r\n			</th>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">I</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">II</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">III</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">IV</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="row" style="text-align:center">1</th>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><strong>Informatica</strong></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>Real</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="row" style="text-align:center">2</th>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><strong>Contabilitate</strong></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>Real</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="row" style="text-align:center">3</th>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><strong>Secretariat şi birotică </strong></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>Umanist</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="row" style="text-align:center">4</th>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><strong>Finanţe</strong></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>Real</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="row" style="text-align:center">5</th>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><strong>Merceologie</strong></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">-</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">-</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">-</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>Real</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th scope="row" style="text-align:center">6</th>\r\n			<td style="text-align:left"><strong>Turism</strong></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">+</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div style="text-align: center;">-</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<div>Umanist</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table></center>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Durata studiilor pentru elevii &icirc;nmatriculaţi &icirc;n baza studiilor gimnaziale (9clase) este de IV ani, iar pentru cei &icirc;nmatriculaţi &icirc;n baza studiilor medii de cultură generală (11 clase) sau a studiilor liceale (BAC) este de II ani. Pentru elevii ce-au fost &icirc;nmatriculaţi &icirc;n colegiu &icirc;n baza studiilor gimnaziale planul de studii la primii III ani de instruire prevede &icirc;n paralel cu studierea disciplilor de specialitate şi a disciplinelor liceale, conform profilului (real sau umanist) La finele anului III de studii această categorie de elevi, pot să se &icirc;nscrie la dorinţă &icirc;n lista candidaţilor pentru susţinerea examenelor de BAC. La anul IV, planul de studii prevede studierea numai a disciplinilor de specialitate. Studiile colegiale finalizează cu susţinerea examenelor de absolvire (de stat) sau susţinerea tezei de licenţă. Diploma de colegiu oferă deţinătorului dreptul de a se angaja &icirc;n c&icirc;mpul muncii şi &icirc;n paralel să-şi aprofundeze cunoştinţele la facultăţile universitare.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Descrierea specialităţilor</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="myTab">\r\n  <li class="active"><a href="#Informatica" data-toggle="tab">Informatica</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href="#Contabilitate" data-toggle="tab">Contabilitate</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href="#Finanţe" data-toggle="tab">Finanţe</a></li>\r\n  <li><a href="#Secretariat" data-toggle="tab">Secretariat şi Birotică</a></li>\r\n   <li><a href="#Turism" data-toggle="tab">Turism</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-content">\r\n<div class="tab-pane active" id="Informatica"><strong>Standardul profesional:</strong> <strong><em>Specialistul este pregătit pentru:</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>stăp&acirc;nirea unui limbaj economic şi tehnic de specialitate necesar pentru activitatea profesională;</li>\r\n	<li>capacitatea de soluţionare a problemelor de proiectare a procedeelor de prelucrare a informaţiilor economice;</li>\r\n	<li>capacitatea de elaborare a resurselor programate aplicativ;</li>\r\n	<li>capacitatea de proiectare şi gestionare a bazelor de date;</li>\r\n	<li>capacitatea de administrare a resurselor tehnice şi programate ale reţelei locale;</li>\r\n	<li>abilitatea de a analiza şi de a soluţiona de sine stătător diverse probleme din domeniul profesional;</li>\r\n	<li>abilitatea de a formula decizii profesionale şi de a le implementa &icirc;n practică;</li>\r\n	<li>abilitatea de a exploata resursele tehnice, programate şi informaţionale ale sistemelor informatice economice.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><em>Oportunităţi de angajare:</em></strong> &Icirc;n calitate de tehnician-programator poate activa la proiectarea, instalarea sistemelor software, inclusiv:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Programator: (consultant &icirc;n organizare şi informatică, tehnician de sistem, tehnician proiectant, programator);</li>\r\n	<li>Tehnician de sistem &ndash; operator: (inginer de sistem hardware, administrator de reţea, administrator de baze de date);</li>\r\n	<li>Tehnician de &icirc;ntreţinere;</li>\r\n	<li>Reprezentant comercial: (responsabil produs, reprezentant marketing, operator v&acirc;nzător).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Contabilitate"><strong>Standardul profesional:</strong> Specialistul este pregătit pentru:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Organizarea şi desfăşurarea relaţiilor financiare;</li>\r\n	<li>Gestionarea contabilităţii la diferite sectoare de evidenţă;</li>\r\n	<li>Elaborarea sistemului de control intern;</li>\r\n	<li>Efectuarea analizei activităţii economico financiare ale unităţii economice.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Competenţe profesionale:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left">La finalizarea studiilor absolventul este capabil:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Să utilizeze reglementările şi actele normative din domeniul contabilităţii, financiar, bancar şi al pieţelor de capital;</li>\r\n	<li>Să ducă evidenţa contabilă a unităţii economice;</li>\r\n	<li>Să elaboreze şi să analizeze rapoartele financiare ale unităţii economice;</li>\r\n	<li>Să efectueze controlul şi auditul intern al unităţii economice;</li>\r\n	<li>Să elaboreze prognoze, programe şi bugete &icirc;n cadrul unităţii economice;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Oportunităţi de angajare:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Contabil &icirc;n instituţii publice, unităţi economice de stat şi private, unităţi comerciale şi de asigurări;</li>\r\n	<li>Operator la ghişeu bancă;</li>\r\n	<li>Operator la ghişeu casă de schimb valutar;</li>\r\n	<li>Casier.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Finanţe">\r\n<div><strong>Domenii de activitate:</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Finanţe, Bănci, Asigurări, Unităţi de producere şi comerţ.</p>\r\n<strong>Standardul profesional:</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>Specialistul este pregătit pentru:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Activitatea de gestiune financiară şi control;</li>\r\n	<li>Dirijarea activităţii financiare ale unităţii economice;</li>\r\n	<li>Organizarea şi desfăşurarea relaţiilor financiare;</li>\r\n	<li>Activitatea &icirc;n cadrul direcţiilor financiare şi instituţiilor de stat, secţiilor financiare ale tuturor tipurilor de agenţi economici;</li>\r\n	<li>Activitatea de economist &icirc;n domeniul financiar.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Competenţe profesionale:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left">La finalizarea studiilor absolventul este capabil:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Să aplice legislaţia &icirc;n vigoare din domeniul finanţe, contabilitate, asigurări, antreprenoriat şi alte domenii;</li>\r\n	<li>Să elaboreze metode de gestiune a resurselor financiare la &icirc;ntreprindere şi &icirc;n cadrul instituţiilor financiare;</li>\r\n	<li>Să evalueze şi să gestioneze eficient resursele proprii şi cele atrase &icirc;n activităţile investiţionale;</li>\r\n	<li>Să studieze indicatorii financiari şi să fundamenteze politica şi strategia de preţuri (tarife) &icirc;n funcţie de conjuncturile pieţei;</li>\r\n	<li>Să aplice tehnici de impunere pentru fiecare tip de impozit şi taxă , să determine obligaţiile fiscale.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Oportunităţi de angajare:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Economist &icirc;n toate departamentele firmelor, departamentele financiare, organele administrării publice locale şi centrale, asigurări;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Agent imobiliar, comercial, fiscal;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Operator la ghişeu bancă;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Inspector de pensii şi asigurări sociale.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Secretariat"><strong>Standardul profesional:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Secretarul-administrator va fi apt să organizeze, administreze serviciul de secretariat &icirc;n instituţii publice, private, unităţi economice etc.;</li>\r\n	<li>Va manifesta toleranţă, respect&acirc;nd deontologia profesională &icirc;n comunicare;</li>\r\n	<li>Va demonstra competenţă profesională;</li>\r\n	<li>Va utiliza tehnologii moderne &icirc;n organizarea activităţii manageriale.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Competenţe profesionale:</strong> La finalizarea studiilor absolventul este capabil să:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Posede cunoştinţe teoretice din domeniul ştiinţelor administrative, juridice, economice;</li>\r\n	<li>Cunoască sistemul administraţiei publice din Republica Moldova;</li>\r\n	<li>Identifice cadrul legislativ din domeniul profesional;</li>\r\n	<li>Utilizeze noile tehnologii informaţionale &icirc;n activităţi practice;</li>\r\n	<li>Demonstreze capacitate de a lua decizii, orientate spre perfecţionarea sistemului de administrare;</li>\r\n	<li>Organizeze &icirc;n mod calificat şi politicos primirea cetăţenilor &icirc;n audienţă, şedinţele de lucru ale administraţiei etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Oportunităţi de angajare:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Referenţi &icirc;n relaţii cu publicul, lucrători &icirc;n arhive;</li>\r\n	<li>Inspectori &icirc;n organele de &icirc;nregistrare a actelor de stare civilă, secretari;</li>\r\n	<li>Specialişti&nbsp; &icirc;n gestiunea resurselor umane, asistenţi ai managerului;</li>\r\n	<li>Lucrători de cancelarie, grefieri &icirc;n instanţele judecătoreşti.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Turism"><strong>Standardul profesional:</strong> Specialistul este pregătit pentru:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Managementul Agenţiilor de turism, reţelelor hoteliere, agro-pensiunilor;</li>\r\n	<li>Efectuarea analizei economico-financiare a Agenţiilor de turism si reţelelor hoteliere;</li>\r\n	<li>Prestarea serviciilor de traducere şi prezentare a itinerarului turistic.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Competenţe profesionale:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left">La finalizarea studiilor absolventul este capabil să:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Valorifice oportunităţi de dezvoltare a turismului şi serviciilor hoteliere;</li>\r\n	<li>Aplice tehnici si strategii de negociere &icirc;n afaceri, metode eficiente de analiză economico-financiară;</li>\r\n	<li>Soluţioneze probleme din domeniul managementului si marketingului &icirc;n activitatea de prestare a serviciilor hoteliere şi a turismului;</li>\r\n	<li>Posede limbi moderne şi capacitatea de organizare, implicare si control a activităţii turistice.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Oportunităţi de angajare:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Manager &icirc;n Agenţii de turism, hoteluri, agro-pensiuni;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Economist &icirc;n Agenţii de turism, reţele hoteliere;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Traducător &icirc;n Agenţii de turism, hoteluri, pensiuni, proiecte turistice;</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align:left">Ghid.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<h1>Specialties</h1>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The college provides the following specialties:</strong></p>\r\n<center><table width="576" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="4" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th scope="row" rowspan="2" width="26">Nr.</th>\r\n<td rowspan="2" width="176">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><strong>The name of the specialty</strong></div>\r\n</td>\r\n<th colspan="4">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><strong>Years</strong><strong> of </strong><strong>study</strong></div>\r\n</th>\r\n<th rowspan="2" width="95">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n<p>High school</p>\r\n<p>syllabus</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</th>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="27">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">I</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="27">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">II</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="21">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">III</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width="28">\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">IV</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: center;">\r\n<th scope="row">1</th>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Informatics</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>sciences</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: center;">\r\n<th scope="row">2</th>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Accounting</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>-</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>sciences</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: center;">\r\n<th scope="row">3</th>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Secretariat and Written Affairs</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>humanities</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: center;">\r\n<th scope="row">4</th>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Finance</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>-</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>sciences</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: center;">\r\n<th scope="row">6</th>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong>Commodity science</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>-</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>-</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>-</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>sciences</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="text-align: center;">\r\n<th scope="row">7</th>\r\n<td style="text-align: left;"><strong><strong>Tourism</strong></strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>+</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>-</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>-</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>humanities</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table></center>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duration of studies for students enrolled on the basis of secondary education (9 forms) is 4 years and on the basis of general secondary education (11forms) or lyceum course (BAC) is 2 years.</p>\r\n<p>Education curriculum during 3 years of studies provides the parallel specialty subjects and high school subjects, according to the syllabus (science or humanities) for the students that have been enrolled at college on the bases of secondary education.</p>\r\n<p>At the end of the III-rd year, students may enter the list of candidates for BAC examinations .</p>\r\n<p>At the IV-th year education curriculum provides only specialty subjects.</p>\r\n<p>The  studies are completed passing graduation examinations (State) or Bachelor&#8217;s thesis.</p>\r\n<h3>Description of  Specialties:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href="#Informatica">Informatics</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="#Contabilitate">Accounting</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="#Finanţe">Finance</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="#Secretariat">Secretariat</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="#Turism">Tourism</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-content">\r\n<div class="tab-pane active" id="Informatica"><strong>Professional standard:</strong> \r\n<p>A future specialist is trained to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> master economic and technical language necessary for     professional activity;</li>\r\n<li> get an ability to solve designing problems of processing procedures of economic information;</li>\r\n<li> get an ability to develop the application  of software resources;</li>\r\n<li> get an ability to design and manage the database;</li>\r\n<li> be able to manage technical resources and programmed local network;</li>\r\n<li> get an ability to analyze and solve problems regarding professional field;</li>\r\n<li> get an ability to make professional decisions and implement them in practice;</li>\r\n<li> be able to exploit the technical resources, scheduled economic information and information systems;</li>\r\n<li> get an ability to exploit  technical,  programmed and information  resources of the economic systems.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Employment opportunities:</em></strong> As a technician &#8211; programmer a graduate can deal with the design, installation of software, including:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>programmer: (IT consultant, computer systems technician, technician-designer, programmer);</li>\r\n<li>system technician &#8211; operator (hardware systems engineer, network administrator, database administrator);</li>\r\n<li>maintenance technician;</li>\r\n<li>commercial representative: (marketing representative, operator seller).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Contabilitate"><strong>Professional standard:</strong>\r\n<p> A future specialist is trained to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> organize and administer(manage) the secretarial service in public, private and business units, etc..</li>\r\n<li>show tolerance and respect professional ethics in communication;</li>\r\n<li>prove professional competence;</li>\r\n<li>Use modern technologies in management activity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Professional skills:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left">Upon graduation the student is able to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>apply theoretical knowledge in the fields of administrative, legal, economic sciences;</li>\r\n<li>identify the public administration system in the Republic of Moldova;</li>\r\n<li>identify the professional legislation;</li>\r\n<li>use modern technologies in professional activity;</li>\r\n<li>prove the ability to make decisions aimed at improving the system of administration;</li>\r\n<li>organize qualified and polite reception of citizens, meetings etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Employment opportunities:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>assistants in public relations, Archive clerks ;</li>\r\n<li>inspectors in the bodies of civil status registration, secretaries;</li>\r\n<li>specialists in human resources management, the assistant manager ;</li>\r\n<li>office workers, clerks in the courts.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Finanţe">\r\n\r\n<strong>Professional standarts:</strong>\r\n\r\n<p>A future specialist is trained to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>perform financial management and control;</li>\r\n<li>manage financial activity of the economic units;</li>\r\n<li>organization and develop financial relations;</li>\r\n<li>perform financial activity within the divisions, state institutions and  financial departments (all types of businesses);</li>\r\n<li>work as an economist in the financial field.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Professional skills:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left">Upon graduation the student is able to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> apply the legislation in force in the field of finance, accounting, insurance, business;</li>\r\n<li> develop methods of financial resources management within the enterprise and financial institutions;</li>\r\n<li> assess and manage own resources and the investment activities;</li>\r\n<li> study the financial indicators and to set the bases of pricing policy/strategy according to the market opportunities;</li>\r\n<li> apply the techniques of assessment for each type of taxes, to determine the tax obligations.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Employment opportunities:</strong></p>\r\n<p>A future specialist is trained to:<strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li> economist in all departments of the economic unit , financial departments, bodies of local and central public administration, insurance;</li>\r\n<li>Real Estate agent , commercial and taxation agent;</li>\r\n<li>bank teller;</li>\r\n<li>inspector of pension and social insurance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Areas</strong><strong> of </strong><strong>activity</strong><strong>: </strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Finance;</li>\r\n<li>Banking;</li>\r\n<li>Insurance;</li>\r\n<li>Units of production and trade.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n		\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Secretariat"><strong>Professional standarts:</strong>\r\n<p>A future specialist is trained to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>&nbsp;organize and administer(manage) the secretarial service in public, private and business units, etc..</li>\r\n<li>show tolerance and respect professional ethics in communication;</li>\r\n<li>prove professional competence;</li>\r\n<li>Use modern technologies in management activity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Professional skills:</strong> Upon graduation the student is able to:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>apply theoretical knowledge in the fields of administrative, legal, economic sciences;</li>\r\n<li>identify the public administration system in the Republic of Moldova;</li>\r\n<li>identify the professional legislation;</li>\r\n<li>use modern technologies in professional activity;</li>\r\n<li>prove the ability to make decisions aimed at improving the system of administration;</li>\r\n<li>organize qualified and polite reception of citizens, meetings etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Employment opportunities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>assistants in public relations, Archive clerks ;</li>\r\n<li>inspectors in the bodies of civil status registration, secretaries;</li>\r\n<li>specialists in human resources management, the assistant manager ;</li>\r\n<li>office workers, clerks in the courts.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class="tab-pane" id="Turism"><strong>Professional standarts:</strong> \r\n<p>A future specialist is trained to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong> </strong>manage travel agencies, hotel networks and rural boarding housing;</li>\r\n<li>perform economic and financial analysis of travel agencies and hotel networks;</li>\r\n<li>provide translation/interpreting services and presentation of the tourist itinerary.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Professional skills:</strong> Upon graduation the student is able to:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>re-valuate the opportunities of tourism and hotel services development;</li>\r\n<li>apply the techniques and strategies of negotiating in business, effective methods of economic-financial analysis;</li>\r\n<li>solve problems in the field of management and marketing of hotel and tourism services;</li>\r\n<li>master modern languages and possess the ability to organize, control and involve the  tourism activity.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:left"><strong>Employment opportunities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong></strong>Manager in travel agencies, hotels, rural boarding houses</li>\r\n<li>Economist in travel agencies, hotel networks;</li>\r\n<li>Interpreting in travel agencies, hotels, boarding houses, tourist projects;</li>\r\n<li>Guide.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n		\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n		', 15),
